      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented QA procedures and version control meets MRL 2 requirement at Gradation 1.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 was used with documented installation qualification, version control, and solver regression tests. QA procedures are compliant with FDA software guidance for simulation tools at MRL 2."
