      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; qualitative demonstration of parameter equivalency between validation and COU is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments use the same FDA benchmark pump geometry and blood-analog fluid as the COU device configuration. Qualitative equivalency is demonstrated; formal parameter equivalency mapping not required at MRL 2."
