    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scope. Validation across five nominal operating points demonstrates CFD predictive capability for hemolysis index within combined uncertainty bounds. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions within the nominal 2–4 L/min, 3000–3500 RPM operating envelope. High-shear-stress blade-tip regions and low-flow near-stall conditions are noted as edge cases studied separately and are not part of this credibility determination.",
